# AI Lab Manual Assistant

## Project Description
AI Lab Manual Assistant is an AI-based tool that helps students quickly find answers from their lab manuals. The system reads a PDF lab manual and allows users to ask questions. It retrieves relevant content from the document and generates answers using the Gemini AI model.

## Features
- Upload lab manual PDF
- Ask questions related to the manual
- AI retrieves relevant information
- Uses LangChain for document processing
- Uses FAISS vector database for fast retrieval
- Works in Google Colab

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Google Colab
- LangChain
- FAISS
- Gemini API
- PyPDF

## How to Run the Project
1. Open the Google Colab notebook.
2. Install required libraries.
3. Add your Gemini API key.
4. Upload the lab manual PDF.
5. Run all cells.
6. Ask questions related to the manual.

